criteria.inclusion_criteria:
1. Severe aplastic anemia;
2. Aged younger than 45 years old;
3. With 9-10/10 HLA matched unrelated donor or 5/6 HLA matched related donor;
4. Life expectancy: more than one month;
5. Sign the informed consent document.

criteria.exclusion_criteria:
1. Congenital bone marrow failure;
2. With HLA matched sibling donor;
3. Severe organ dysfunction: serum ALT more than 3 times ULN, Ccr less than 60ml/min, left ventricular ejection fraction less than 50%.
